  "chapter": {
    "children": [
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "tag": "v",
            "num": "1",
            "text": "I said, “Now listen,"
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "you leaders of Jacob"
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "and rulers of the house of Israel:"
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "Is it not right for you to understand justice?"
          },
          {
            "tag": "v",
            "num": "2",
            "text": "You who hate good"
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "and love evil,"
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "you who tear off their skin,"
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "their flesh from their bones—"
          },
          {
            "tag": "v",
            "num": "3",
            "text": "you who also eat the flesh of my people,"
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "and tear their skin off,"
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "break their bones,"
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "and chop them in pieces,"
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "just like meat for a pot,"
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "just like meat in a cauldron."
          },
          {
            "tag": "v",
            "num": "4",
            "text": "Then you rulers will cry out to Yahweh,"
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "but he will not answer you."
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "He will hide his face from you at that time,"
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "because you have done evil deeds.”"
          },
          {
            "tag": "v",
            "num": "5",
            "text": "Yahweh says this,"
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "“As for the prophets who lead my people astray,"
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "if one gives them something to eat,"
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "they proclaim, ‘Peace.’"
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "But if he puts nothing in their mouths,"
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "they dedicate themselves to wage war on him."
          },
          {
            "tag": "v",
            "num": "6",
            "text": "Therefore, it will be night for you with no vision for you;"
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "it will be dark so that you will do no divination."
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "The sun will go down on the prophets,"
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "and the day will be dark on them."
          },
          {
            "tag": "v",
            "num": "7",
            "text": "The seers will be put to shame,"
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "and the diviners will be confused."
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "All of them will cover their lips,"
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "for there is no answer from me.”"
          },
          {
            "tag": "v",
            "num": "8",
            "text": "But as for me, I am full of power by the Spirit of Yahweh,"
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "and am full of justice and might,"
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "to declare to Jacob his transgression,"
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "and to Israel his sin."
          },
          {
            "tag": "v",
            "num": "9",
            "text": "Now listen to this,"
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "you leaders of the house of Jacob,"
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "and rulers of the house of Israel,"
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "you who detest justice,"
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "and pervert everything right."
          },
          {
            "tag": "v",
            "num": "10",
            "text": "You build Zion with blood"
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "and Jerusalem with iniquity."
          },
          {
            "tag": "v",
            "num": "11",
            "text": "Your leaders judge for a bribe,"
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "your priests teach for a price,"
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "and your prophets do divination for money."
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "Yet you rely on Yahweh and say,"
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "“Is not Yahweh with us?"
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "No evil will come on us.”"
          },
          {
            "tag": "v",
            "num": "12",
            "text": "Therefore, because of you,"
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "Zion will become a plowed field,"
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "Jerusalem will become a heap of rubble,"
          },
          {
            "tag": "q",
            "text": "and the hill of the temple will become a thicket."
          }
        ],
        "tag": "m"
      }
    ],
    "num": 3
  },
